{"pageProps":{"caseData":{"id":"gts","contentHtml":"<p>Global Traffic Systems was a notable European player in the field of traffic\nmanagement. The company specialized in developing practical software and\nhardware solutions to enhance road traffic efficiency. Its contributions, such\nas tools for traffic light coordination and real-time traffic monitoring\nsystems, brought tangible improvements to daily commuting.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend Development: Designed and implemented dynamic, real-time UI's for traffic control using JavaScript, React, SASS, and REST APIs, ensuring responsive performance and scalability.</li>\n<li>UX Optimization: Enhanced operator workflows by creating intuitive UI/UX solutions improving decision-making processes in high-stakes environments.</li>\n<li>Data Integration: Worked closely with backend teams to integrate live traffic data and IoT sensor inputs into user-facing interfaces.</li>\n<li>Website Development: Led the development of the company’s website, ensuring mobile-first design and cross-platform compatibility.</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"Emblem of Global Traffic Systems\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/Logo.jpg\">\n    <figcaption>Corporate Identity: The GTS's Logo</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"GTS Web App Interface\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/shot.png\">\n    <figcaption>Corporate Interface of the GTS Web Platform</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<video controls>\n  <source src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/lubin.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n</video>\n<video controls>\n  <source src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/2.5min.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n</video>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"Overview of Products &#x26; Services\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/GTS-Products.png\">\n    <figcaption>GTS's Comprehensive Catalogue of Products &#x26; Services</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"Detailed Product Synopsis\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/GTS-Product-1.png\">\n    <figcaption>Thorough Presentation of a GTS Product Offering</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"Functional Blueprint\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/GTS-Product-2.png\">\n    <figcaption>Product Functionality Described with Precision</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n    <img alt=\"Technical Configurations\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/GTS-Product-3.png\">\n    <figcaption>Detail-Oriented Technical Specifications</figcaption>\n</figure>","currentNum":10,"totalCases":14,"prevCase":{"id":"eleek","title":"E-bike Store","team":"Star Way · Web Agency","date":"2021-03-21","lang":"en","size":"L","tags":["UX/UI","Design"],"country":"Ukraine","cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/eleek/shot1.png","description":"UI/UX Design for an Ukrainian online e-bike store"},"nextCase":{"id":"cookbook","title":"CookBook","date":"2020-08-02","lang":"en","size":"L","tags":["UX/UI","Design"],"country":"","cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/cookbook/cover.jpg","description":"Interactive Food Preparation Assistance"},"title":"Global Traffic Systems","date":"2020-10-21","lang":"en","size":"L","tags":["UX/UI","Design","Development","Front-end"],"country":"Poland","cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/echo-vladimir/portfolio/main/public/media/gts/Logo.jpg","description":"Urban traffic management solutions"}},"__N_SSG":true}